===Noun===
# A [[mechanical]] or [[electrical]] device for moving [[air]].
# Anything resembling a fan in shape, e.g. a [[peacock]]'s [[tail]].
# An [[admirer]] or [[aficionado]], especially of a [[sport]] or [[performer]].  (Shortened form of ''[[fanatic]]'')

====Translations====
*[[German]]: [[Fächer]] ''m'' (1, 2), [[Gebläse]] ''n'' (1), Fan ''m'' (3)

===Transitive verb===
# To [[blow]] air on (something), using a fan.

====Translations====
*[[German]]: [[anfachen]]

===Intransitive verb===
# (Usually with ''out'') To [[move]] or [[spread]] in multiple [[direction]]s from one point.

====Translations====
*[[German]]: [[auffächern]], [[umwehen]]